-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/sanofi-sa-sells-1-billion-1-2-3-year-sr-unsecured-notes.html
The following issue went on sale today:  Issuer:      Sanofi SA
Manager(s):  Bank of America Merrill Lynch  Citigroup Global Markets Inc  Deutsche Bank Securities Inc  Natixis/New York
Amount:      $1 billion
Coupon:      1.2 percent
Maturity:    Sept. 30, 2014
Settlement:  Sept. 30, 2011
Spread:      83 basis points more than governments
 